{"tid":590936,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"點resign好？","createTime":"2018-03-13T05:42:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T19:37:17.000Z","uid":30368,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4ab00bc8646b9c3a5d65adadb08a2ae65a970af3","tid":590936,"uid":30368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T05:42:00.000Z","msg":"講講背景先<br />\n工程公司，個老細痴撚線既，小小野都捉入房瘋狂抽插<br />\n人工幾好，比出面高一截<br />\nOffice同事個個都好nice<br />\n我做左3年嗌左2次resign，第1次係自己想唔做，但比人留低左<br />\n第2次係我出面有offer，不過要3個月後，而家呢間公司請左人叫我教，教完之後比offer我果間公司又話唔要人，我就又留返低係度做<br />\n到而家就係第3次喇....<br />\n話說點解想嗌resign呢，就係因為發覺自己係呢度做大錯唔小，小錯不斷咁，次次都搞到麻麻煩煩咁，做左幾年都仲係咁，我就想索性唔做喇<br />\n但係而家我唔知點resign好，講實話上年我咁樣，老細同高層都唔介意，而家過左大半年就又話走，咁樣真係好難走得開"},{"pid":"9016f0b84bc5c447389b50fcacae562cca510f8e","tid":590936,"uid":45645,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T09:19:21.000Z","msg":"tell the boss, go fuxk yourself, i am quit now."},{"pid":"b03ba25cd207e0a72bb59ac77fccf938acf0e6e7","tid":590936,"uid":172060,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T15:02:55.000Z","msg":"你係堅持要走既話無人留到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔洗在意高層點睇你 最緊要自己好受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a255611d16b018fd0d0dbac295ed28cd571db53b","tid":590936,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T17:03:49.000Z","msg":"consultant?"},{"pid":"208001ce79ff56b7198f0792ec7d68a17c8fd5a9","tid":590936,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T17:13:14.000Z","msg":"唔中意就走啦,勉強冇幸福"},{"pid":"76745106528919ee67440cd641af44749a32a236","tid":590936,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T17:42:30.000Z","msg":"做咁耐都仲成日錯又有比市價高人工 你老細都唔炒你算好好"},{"pid":"e300e3a7cec765027aa6f7407e5171797b4683ad","tid":590936,"uid":10490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T19:37:17.000Z","msg":"企硬+遞信走<br />\n無人迫到你"}]}